unpublishedAction.name: myFunStoreValues

actionConfiguration.body:
() => {
if (vayCountryofRegistration.selectedOptionValue === "IN"){
		storeValue( "vayApplicantRole", vayRoleSelection.selectedOptionValue)
		storeValue( "vayApplicantName", vayApplicantName.text)
		storeValue( "vayApplicantMobile", vayApplicantMobile.text)
		storeValue( "vayApplicantEmail", vayApplicantEmail.text)
		storeValue( "vayCountryofRegistration", vayCountryofRegistration.selectedOptionValue)
	storeValue( "vayCountryofRegistrationCode",vayCountryofRegistration.selectedOptionValue.split('|')[0])
storeValue( "customerIsIndForeign","E_REGISTERED_INDIAN")
storeValue( "customerCorpNonCorp","IndianCorporate")
//Check if OID exist to handle modify flow else create new customer flow
		
storeValue("customerOID",JSGenerateID.myFungenerateOID())

storeValue("customerID", JSGenerateID.myFungenerateCOID())

storeValue("customerParticipantID",JSGenerateID.myFungenerateCPID())
		
//console.log(appsmith.store.customerOID);
		navigateTo('Application Form - India',{})
	}
	else{
		storeValue( "vayApplicantJurisdiction", vayCountryofRegistration.selectedOptionValue)
		storeValue( "vayApplicantRole", vayRoleSelection.selectedOptionValue)
storeValue( "vayApplicantRole", vayRoleSelection.selectedOptionValue)
		storeValue( "vayApplicantName", vayApplicantName.text)
		storeValue( "vayApplicantMobile", vayApplicantMobile.text)
		storeValue( "vayApplicantEmail", vayApplicantEmail.text)
		storeValue( "vayCountryofRegistration", vayCountryofRegistration.selectedOptionValue)
		storeValue( "vayCountryofRegistrationCode",vayCountryofRegistration.selectedOptionValue.split('|')[0])
storeValue( "customerIsIndForeign","E_REGISTERED_ABORAD")
storeValue( "customerCorpNonCorp","Foreign")
	
//Check if OID exist to handle modify flow else create new customer flow
		
storeValue("customerOID",JSGenerateID.myFungenerateOID())

storeValue("customerID", JSGenerateID.myFungenerateCOID())

storeValue("customerParticipantID",JSGenerateID.myFungenerateCPID())
		navigateTo('Application Form - Foreign',{})
	}
}
